@startuml
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

rectangle "Client Application" as Client
rectangle "API Gateway" as Gateway
rectangle "Quota Service" as Quota
rectangle "Billing Service" as Billing
rectangle "Rate Limiter" as RateLimiter
rectangle "Gemini API" as Gemini

Client --> Gateway : API Request
Gateway --> Quota : Check Quota
Quota --> Billing : Verify Billing
Quota --> RateLimiter : Enforce Limits
RateLimiter --> Gemini : Forward Request
Gemini --> RateLimiter : Response
RateLimiter --> Gateway : Response
Gateway --> Client : Response

note right of Quota
  Quota exceeded:
  - Input tokens
  - Model: gemini-2.0-flash
  - Location: global
  - Retry after 23s
end note
@enduml